        "last_activity_date": 1526315401,
        "creation_date": 1461766103,
        "answer_count": 2,
        "title": "How to convert java.util.stream.Stream&lt;Something&gt; into kotlin.Sequence&lt;Something&gt;",
        "body": "<p>Java 8 Streams are powerful but when parallelism is not needed Kotlin Sequence seems to be simpler to use.<\/p>\n\n<p>Is there a way to convert a <code>stream.sequencial()<\/code> into a Sequence?<\/p>\n",
        "question_id": 36892291,
        "tags": [
            "java",
            "java-stream",
            "kotlin"
        ],
        "score": 16,
        "accepted_answer_id": 47889522,
